description: More markets for the Coupe de France game, scheduled for March 5 at 3:10 PM ET.

markets.description:
In the upcoming Coupe de France game, scheduled for March 5 at 3:10 PM ET:

This market will resolve to "Olympique Lyonnais" if Olympique Lyonnais win the game by 3 or more goals.

Otherwise, this market will resolve to "Racing Club de Lens".

If the game is postponed, this market will remain open until the game has been completed. If the game is canceled entirely, with no make-up game, this market will resolve 50–50.

This market will resolve according to the official final score published on fff.fr. This market refers only to the outcome within the first 90 minutes of regular play plus stoppage time.

The primary resolution source for this market is the official statistics of the event as recognized by the governing body or event organizers. However, if the governing body or event organizers have not published final match statistics within 2 hours after the event's conclusion, a consensus of credible reporting may be used instead.
